title: Google Withdraws As Host Of Democratic Fundraising Event
content: Daily Caller, by Eric Lieberman Posted By: JoniTx- Sat, 02 09 2018 09:09:14 GMT Google was set to rent out its D.C. headquarters to a progressive group running a fundraiser for top Senate Democrats, but canceled it Friday just days before. The group Run For Something cultivates up'and'coming Democrats for all levels of government. Its event, Party For Something, was supposed to occur June 6 at a location only disclosed if tickets ($100 to $1,000) were purchased. (Photo) Important note! Confirmation of the date, time, and venue will be in your donation receipt, reads the website, which also says Location available upon RSVP elsewhere. No need to print anything; just check in with ID
